I've seen rants on this board that was for little things but rest assured, my respect for Elder Blades hasn't gone up after this because they removed a member that &quot;KSed&quot; ( attacked a mob that was engaged or not? ), but down because it's a clear sign of intolerance. And in this game you must have some tolerance. <p><CENTER><A HREF="http://ak.lonelygamer.com">
